## Operating Rules
- never treat micro completion as macro completion;
- every upward synthesis must preserve evidence and uncertainty;
- loop back when verification finds a defect.

## Operating Rules
- final-system surfaces establish current implementation truth;
- binding locks govern decisions where implementation is silent;
- staging and research remain evidence-only;
- conflicts are exposed, not averaged.

## Operating Rules
- roles are accountability, not permission;
- operational state is explicit;
- every agent has a bounded surface and default validator;
- overlap must preserve ownership boundaries.
